title: The World Owes You Nothing, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO60
description: Most people don't understand that the world owes them nothing. They are selfish and suffer from a massive sense of entitlement. People who rise above the common lot and achieve alpine heights of success are those who put others first, care, and provide value.
